{"tid":996533,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟笑人喺學校廁所屙屎嘅文化係點嚟？","createTime":"2019-01-26T11:06:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-27T17:42:53.000Z","uid":199292,"like":1534,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":110,"replies":[{"pid":"9545cfc0c789a187fd20dced7ccc407b3d60e020","tid":996533,"uid":199292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T11:06:14.000Z","msg":"唔知由幾時開始 不論小學 初中<br />\n當有人被發現喺廁所屙屎 總會有班戇鳩仔<br />\n就算唔識嘅都會指住嚟笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係認真恥笑<br />\n以前喺親學校屙屎要望清楚有冇人先<br />\n好似偷嘢咁走入個廁格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去到高form反而低form唔敢搞你<br />\n同輩嘅都唔會點笑<br />\n屙屎明明人之常情 幾時開始搞到咁尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe15e5320e1f9ac7a240b4e0f54f57de5ec787d3","tid":996533,"uid":218575,"like":1395,"dislike":3,"score":1392,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T11:07:21.000Z","msg":"係以前細個幼稚 先會笑啫<br />\n大個啲就唔會 <br />\n會同frd直接講好撚急屎<br />\n去屙個緊屎先"},{"pid":"6d44eca8d627a42ef61759bb66ec052f9175d055","tid":996533,"uid":138732,"like":629,"dislike":5,"score":624,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T11:11:42.000Z","msg":"唔會笑 <br />\n<br />\n不過會提心吊膽驚俾人爆門或者淋水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06ed58c11a6211ee5301011bacb7fab3354e68db","tid":996533,"uid":199292,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"quote":{"pid":"fe15e5320e1f9ac7a240b4e0f54f57de5ec787d3","tid":996533,"uid":218575,"like":1395,"dislike":3,"score":1392,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T11:07:21.000Z","msg":"係以前細個幼稚 先會笑啫<br />\n大個啲就唔會 <br />\n會同frd直接講好撚急屎<br />\n去屙個緊屎先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T11:12:42.000Z","msg":"直接講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08167bf959a153d782f72ac23b4db68e3f4c547d","tid":996533,"uid":208159,"like":357,"dislike":7,"score":350,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T11:14:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d1512d075a97ecde43ee5b60338af8c696fc30ca","tid":996533,"uid":136190,"like":2